description:
Source: CD + Fresh Cover Art Scan

Have never heard of Miki but her voice and style is amazing and can't help but wonder why she isn't well-known. These are songs by Billie but expect a more jazzy R&B flavor like you are sitting in a piano bar on a 2nd date and you just know things are going to end well.

- Big Papi
